---
title: Classic Beef Meatloaf with Cheddar-Chive Smashed Potatoes and Roasted Broccoli
description: Meatloaf is a classic dish that gets a tasty update in this recipe. This rendition is made tender with breadcrumbs and sweetened with a ketchup glaze. Paired with creamy, cheesy mash and roasted broccoli, you won't be able to decide which part of this meal you like best!
